# 🌄 Image Gallery Web App

A modern, responsive, and dynamic **Image Gallery Website** built using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**, powered by the **Unsplash API**.

---

## 🚀 Live Demo

🌍 http://127.0.0.1:5500/index.html

---

## 📸 Features

✨ Clean & modern UI  
🔍 Search images using Unsplash API  
🎯 Filter images by category (Nature, City, Food)  
🖼 Dynamic image loading  
⚡ Fast & smooth animations  
🔐 Login popup interface  
📱 Fully responsive (mobile + desktop)  
🎨 Hover effects & transitions  

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- HTML5  
- CSS3  
- JavaScript (Vanilla JS)  
- Unsplash API  

